Package com.palantir.ptoss.cinch.swing

Classes used to bind Swing components to BindableModel objects.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Action.Wiring Inner utility class used to wire Action bindings.
Bound.Utilities Inner utility class to simplify figuring out how to display null values in controls.
Bound.Wiring Inner utility class that performs the runtime wiring of all bindings in this package.
BoundExtent.Wiring Inner utility class that performs the runtime wiring of all BoundExtent bindings.
BoundLocation.Wiring Inner utility class that performs the runtime wiring of all BoundLocation bindings.
BoundSelection.Wiring Inner utility class that performs the runtime wiring of all BoundSelection bindings.
EnabledIf.Wiring Inner utility class that performs the runtime wiring of all EnabledIf bindings.
JCheckBoxWiringHarness A WiringHarness for binding a JCheckBox to a boolean value in a BindableModel.
JComboBoxWiringHarness A WiringHarness for binding a JComboBox to a List value in a BindableModel.
JLabelWiringHarness A WiringHarness for binding a JLabel to a value in a BindableModel.
JListWiringHarness Wires up a JList to a List in a BindableModel.
JPasswordFieldWiringHarness A WiringHarness for binding a JPasswordField to a value in a BindableModel.
JProgressBarWiringHarness A WiringHarness for binding a JProgressBar to an int value in a BindableModel.
JSliderWiringHarness A WiringHarness for binding a JSlider to an Integer value in a BindableModel.
JTextComponentWiringHarness A WiringHarness for binding a JTextComponent to a String value in a BindableModel.
JToggleButtonWiringHarness A WiringHarness for binding a JToggleButton to an Enum value in a BindableModel.
OnChange.Wiring Inner utility class that performs the runtime wiring of all OnChange bindings.
OnClick.Wiring Inner utility class that performs the runtime wiring of all OnClick bindings.
OnFocusChange.Wiring Inner utility class that performs the runtime wiring of all OnFocusChange bindings.
VisibleIf.Wiring Inner utility class that performs the runtime wiring of all VisibleIf bindings.
 

Enum Summary
EnabledIf.Type Enum to specify if normal or inverted comparisons should be used.
OnClick.Button Enum specifying which mouse button is being bound by this binding.
VisibleIf.Type Enum to specify if normal or inverted comparisons should be used.
 

Annotation Types Summary
Action A component binding that will call a method when an action occurs.
Bound Used to bind a UI control to a model property, where property is meant in a strict Java sense.
BoundExtent A binding for an interface component that has an extent (setExtent/getExtent methods).
BoundLocation A binding for an interface component that has a location (setLocation/getLocation methods).
BoundSelection A binding for an interface component that has a selection like a JList or JComboBox.
EnabledIf A binding that will set the enabled state of the annotated component to the state of a model boolean.
OnChange A component binding that will call a method when an action occurs.
OnClick A binding that will call a method when the on-click action occurs on this component.
OnFocusChange A binding that will call one method when the bound component loses focus, and another method when focus is gained.
VisibleIf A binding that will set the Visible state of the annotated component to the state of a model boolean.
 

Package com.palantir.ptoss.cinch.swing Description

Classes used to bind Swing components to BindableModel objects.
